channel.description:
Thank you for all your nominations recently! Lets get straight into the Polls. The polling will be available until January 4th at Midnight.
**Favorite Auxy Track** [poll type=regular results=on_close chartType=bar] * Bloom by AZHR * Golden Dust by Genesis * Sigiwb by Phluze * Making Noise by Paroxyzm * Goodtimes by FlynnT * Glow Tide by Peregrihn * Earthquake by Austin Haga * Awaken by Stereofield * Stranger by Auxysimon * Runaways by Brighid * Chrysalism by Mr. Moo * Safe Haven by BSJ * The Call by Mr. Anderson * Restless by Obio [/poll]
**Favorite Auxy Producer** [poll name=poll2 type=regular results=on_close chartType=bar] * MrSerpent * Kayasho * PISTOL * Asis_4591 * NotMIles * Mr.Moo * A_L_E_X * Crystaldawn * FlynnT * Arimyth * Heniel * Produk * Mvtt * Phluze [/poll] **Most Innovative Track** [poll name=poll3 type=regular results=on_close chartType=bar] * Cutting Through by Toxic Caves * Power Trip by Toxic Caves * chroma by Anechoik * insanity by PISTOL * Red Skies by Austin Haga * Vials by NotMiles * Sigiwb by Phluze * Corridors by NotMiles * Home by Unfound * PARADISE '87 by Toxic Caves * Sunburst by Tornait * Soon by Austin Haga * お元気ですか by Anechoik * Future by The Osprey * Maze by Phluze/Blackocean [/poll] **Supportive Individual** [poll name=poll4 type=regular results=on_close chartType=bar] * Akyut * averageteencuber * kheeshKP * Twizard * Tom Heck (Hex) * Arimyth * MrSerpent * Mr.Moo * Hum4n01d * MR_ANDERSON * The Osprey * chromaanimator * Literally Everyone * INDIR3CT's Mom [/poll] [Fyi Literally Everyone and INDIR3CT's Mom are irrelevant]
